<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Voucher Template</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            page-break-after: always;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .signature {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 20mm;
            width: 100%;
            padding-right: 20mm;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .page {
            width: 303mm;
            height: 216mm;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 20mm;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .voucher {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 5px double #fff;
            background-image: url('https://www.qrsong.io/assets/images/cards_homepage.jpg?v=1');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20mm;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .voucher-header {
            font-size: 56px;
            font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 10mm;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        .voucher-content {
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 10mm;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10mm;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .voucher-footer {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #000000;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 5mm;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10mm;
        }
        .qr-code {
            width: 50mm;
            height: 50mm;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 10mm;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="voucher">
            <div class="voucher-header">QRSong Credit Voucher</div>
            <div class="voucher-content">
                <p>Congratulations! You've received a special QRSong credit voucher.</p>
                <p>Use this voucher to unlock exclusive music experiences.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10mm;">XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX</p>
                <div class="qr-code">
                    <p>QR Code Here</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="voucher-footer">Valid until: [Expiration Date]</div>
            <div class="signature">Authorized Signature</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="voucher">
            <div class="voucher-content">
                <p>Terms and Conditions:</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
